This paper is likely to belong to the Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC) sub-category as it focuses on understanding user needs and challenges with a specific tool. The use of online forums to collect data also suggests a potential overlap with Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Database (cs.DB) sub-categories. The discussion of implications for next-generation software design suggests a potential overlap with Software Engineering (cs.SE) and Cybersecurity (cs.CY) sub-categories.
